{"tid":686203,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"聲演1/4世紀　小新配音員辭演《蠟筆小新》","createTime":"2018-06-01T04:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T04:10:12.000Z","uid":59966,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35041238b1bf2003970cfe894e05e80b07706a1e","tid":686203,"uid":59966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180601/mobile/bkn-20180601115407002-0601_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180601%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180601115407002-0601_00862_001.html&d=N%2BywAU3rtOvD%2FF0MpcDFvjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=da10d0c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180601/mobile/bkn-20180601115407002-0601_00862_001.html</a><br />\n日本長青動畫《蠟筆小新》的配音員矢島晶子，今日宣布退出聲演超過26年的主角野原新之助。負責播映《蠟筆小新》的朝日電視台發聲明，表示6月29日播出的《蠟筆小新》，會是由矢島晶子聲演的最後一集，之後會另覓配音員聲演小新一角。 <br />\n<br />\n已屆51歲的矢島晶子，自1992年4月13日起參與《蠟筆小新》的配音工作，足足聲演主角小新逾26年零3個月。矢島晶子表示要離開「野原家」，因自己對維持小新聲線日漸感到困難，有感難以自然表現出角色，故主動向電視台提出請辭。而電視台對矢島長年以聲音為小新給予生命的功績，表示感謝。 <br />\n<br />\n廣志轉完 到小新又要轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed64e01e3a4bd1aa14596897c2b906ecf2e6fe7b","tid":686203,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fee40aad66172dd25c41e4f34e357f8c39e679","tid":686203,"uid":83328,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:04:49.000Z","msg":"最恐怖係，悟空個配音仲未退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八十幾歲阿婆仲哈咩哈咩哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ba